episodes.title: Man alleges tree is being killed off by '5G transmitter'
episodes.description:
Footage shows one side of a tree 'completely dead' while the other is still healthy

A man points out how the dying side of the tree is feet away from a street light

He claims a '5G transmitter' located inside the light is to blame for the dead tree 

However others have pointed out that tree rot or wildlife could be to blame
